Converting Next ninja list to TS


https://nextjs.org/docs/basic-features/typescript

converting an existing next js into TS

npm install next@latest -- if next app was created long ago
npm upgrade react@latest react-dom@latest

npm install --save-dev typescript @types/react
 npm install --save-dev @types/react
 npm install --save-dev @types/node
 
 
 then npm run dev to detect ts 
 this will initialize a tsconfig
 
 in tsconfig -
"moduleResolution": "Node",


convert js files to tsx

create interfaces

type getStaticProps, Paths and ServerSide

type response from api before passing to component as props

type the props passed

type api if needed

type props passed to children if any

type Layout component
